&lt;p data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;DoorDash is looking for top-talent to help grow our New Zealand New Verticals business! We&#39;re looking for experienced individuals with deep retail market knowledge to allow us to best serve our consumers, Dashers, and merchants. Join our never-ending pursuit to better power economies in New Zealand and across the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;heading&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;strong&quot;&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;DoorDash is looking for an Enterprise Partnerships Lead to join the &lt;strong data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;strong&quot;&gt;New Verticals Business Development&lt;/strong&gt; team, to sign net new retailers in New Zealand. You will be responsible for selling DoorDash’s full suite of products to retailers across our New Verticals categories, including general merchandise, as well as emerging verticals such as pets, fashion, beauty, hardware, consumer electronics, and more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;You will report to the Director of New Verticals Business Development, ANZ. This role is hybrid with 3 days in-office and 2 days remote / meeting and pitching to prospective partners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;heading&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;strong&quot;&gt;You’re excited about this opportunity because you will…&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Leverage your experience and network previously dealing with New Zealand’s largest retailers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Develop the tactical strategy for engaging each retailer in the sales pipeline, including the largest retailers in the country&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Successfully negotiate and close retail partnerships across our suite of products, including Marketplace and White-Label Deliveries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-nod

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;display: none; max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://click.appcast.io/greenhouse-te8/a31.png?ent=34&amp;amp;e=22630&amp;amp;t=1701374353806&quot; width=&quot;1px&quot;&gt; &lt;img style=&quot;display: none; max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://track.jobadx.com/v1/i.gif?utm_pixel=224e990b-8ff4-4287-8d5d-2ff09647f181&amp;amp;utm_ptz=EST&amp;amp;utm_rqt=track&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of our Commerce Platform business, the In-Store Sales team at DoorDash is responsible for driving growth for some of the top restaurants in the APAC by empowering them with innovative in-store technology solutions to create best in class guest experiences. This team plays a critical role in expanding our merchant partnerships beyond existing channels and delivering seamless, high-impact experiences for consumers in-store.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work in close collaboration with cross-functional partners across Sales Development, Account Management, Product, and Strategy &amp;amp; Operations to bring cutting-edge solutions to life—enabling our merchants to thrive in a hybrid digital and physical environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As &lt;strong&gt;Head of Sales, In Store&lt;/strong&gt;, you will lead a team of sales professionals focused on growing our in-store business across key merchant segments. You’ll be responsible for managing managers and their respective teams, setting vision and strategy, and driving execution to deliver against aggressive revenue and adoption targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will report to the Senior Director of Sales for DoorDash Commerce Platform and serve as a key leader in scaling our newest frontier in merchant engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’re excited about this opportunity because you will…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead a high-impact team:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage and mentor a team of Sales Managers and their sales representatives focused on in-store product adoption across strategic accounts and regions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive strategy and execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop, implement, and continuously refine go-to-market strategies for DoorDash’s in-store offerings, ensuring alignment with company goals and merchant needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Product, Strategy &amp;amp; Operations, Sales Development, and Account Management teams to identify opportunities, refine solutions, and optimize customer experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhance team performance:&lt;/strong&gt; Cultivate a culture of performance, ownership, and inclusivity. Prioritize the development and engagement of your team to support long-term success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovate and optimize:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify trends and operational inefficiencies. Design and implement scalable solutions, processes, and tools that increase effectiveness and streamline adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stay merchant-obsessed:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage direct merchant insights and field feedback to improve offerings and influence product development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’re excited about you because…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have &lt;strong&gt;10+ years of sales experience&lt;/strong&gt;, including exceeding performance targets and building successful pipeline strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You bring &lt;strong&gt;6+ years of people management experience&lt;/strong&gt;, with a strong record of leading managers and developing high-performing teams.&lt;/li&gt;
