&lt;p&gt;Our ANZ Sales team drives DoorDash&#39;s growth across Australia and New Zealand. The team has built strong momentum through disciplined execution, structural simplification, and record-breaking performance across topline growth, merchant investment, and sales productivity. As we scale into our next phase, the strength of our strategy and operations function must grow with it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Head of Sales Strategy &amp;amp; Operations for ANZ, you&#39;ll own the strategy and execution engine behind our entire sales organization across all verticals and segments. This means designing go-to-market playbooks, building sales forecasting and incentive frameworks, optimizing merchant acquisition and investment motions, and driving cross-functional initiatives that improve how we sell, what we sell, and who we sell to. You&#39;ll be responsible for turning market intelligence and commercial insights into operating plans that drive sustainable, profitable growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who is analytical, commercially sharp, and energized by building structure in a fast-moving, competitive market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hybrid role with 3 days a week in office and 2 days remote.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’re excited about this opportunity because you will…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
