&lt;li&gt;Drive impact measurement across sales initiatives, building the analytical infrastructure to understand what&#39;s working, quantify incrementality, and scale what drives results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and lead a high-performing team, coaching and developing strategy and operations talent while fostering a culture of ownership, analytical rigor, and cross-functional partnership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accelerate productivity through AI, identifying and deploying AI-powered workflows, rep enablement tools, and process automation that make the sales org faster and smarter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
