&lt;p data-start=&quot;177&quot; data-end=&quot;435&quot;&gt;Join our Advertising &amp;amp; Promotions Strategy and Operations team which operates at the intersection of e-commerce and advertising, surfacing and monetising relevant content that benefits our core audiences. We provide digital solutions that help advertisers effectively reach DoorDash audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;437&quot; data-end=&quot;738&quot;&gt;This role is responsible for driving the operations and performance of some of our newest and fastest-growing Ads &amp;amp; Promos offerings across Australia and New Zealand. It sits within the global team, which owns operations and performance globally, with a specific focus on the ANZ markets.&lt;/p&gt;
