&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with Product, Engineering, Data Science and other tech teams to release new features &amp;amp; products, monitor product adoption, and unblock obstacles and technical challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Devise the appropriate go-to-market playbooks. Enable teams through market-relevant training, product releases, sales collateral, reporting, and benchmarking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
