&lt;p&gt;At DoorDash, the Data Science and Analytics team uncovers insights and translates them into actionable recommendations that drive decisions across the organisation. Analytics is integral to all areas of DoorDash, and this role sits within the global team with a specific focus on the ANZ markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Data Science and Analytics team is looking for a Marketing Analytics Manager to guide measurement, strategy, and decision-making across our Australia and New Zealand Marketing efforts. This is an individual contributor role that will take strong ownership of projects and drive them to completion, collaborating with a range of cross-functional teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some of the impactful projects you will work on include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep diving into results from digital A/B tests to generate insights that improve marketing performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analysing campaign results and presenting insights to leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exploring our customer base to identify target segments and optimise marketing strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scaling measurement and reporting solutions to set us up for future success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You&#39;re excited about this opportunity because you will…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a trusted thought partner to our Marketing, Finance, and Executive teams, helping shape decisions on ‘what’s next’ for DoorDash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and analyse experiments to measure the ROI of our digital marketing spend and develop actionable recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate insights on customer segments and our most valuable consumers to identify opportunities to improve marketing performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with agencies and third-party vendors to develop and implement measurement solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to global reporting on the impact of brand marketing campaigns to inform channel investment decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI to develop tools and workflows that enable marketing stakeholders to self-serve and democratise insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
